channel.title: How do others log into my private server
channel.description:
I hit compile. It says Fuzzardscape blah blah blah at 0.0.0.0:43594 or something. I can login. I type in localhost. I use no-ip. I open no-ip duc, and the face is smiling. I've done everything the tuts say except the port forwarding thingy. Friends try to connect, but they can't. It says the server is offline.
BTW, on the port forward website, I found my router, then a list of programs comes up. I don't know what to do from there.
